com.nv.security
Class SecurityToken

java.lang.Object
  com.nv.security.SecurityToken

public class SecurityToken
extends java.lang.Object

A valud object designed to manage security information as it relates to the application environment and the logged on user.

The security token represents an authenticated user and is used to gain access to various resources pertaining to the Launch Pad application.

Author:
rterrell
